casebody.data:
Friday, March 2, 2001

MOTION DOCKET

99-1420. State ex rel. Myers v. Brown.

In Quo Warranto. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of quo warranto. Upon consideration of the motion to quash subpoena for attendance of witness and for production of documentary evidence,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, granted.
